ps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bsavc5l9QR4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dbsavc5l9QR4&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5Au0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=1ead9fd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bsavc5l9QR4</a>"},{"pid":"f1ed9ca58886cbb5c6f6655ae217541938b0bd24","tid":1513181,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"0b8cb6a9aee9c2379bff861320d529a4d849d9c3","tid":1513181,"uid":131264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c2e3517b7b4018fe93c2a2f021ea200319624bd","tid":1513181,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"用錄音，通街播，人走咗都可以留低個喇叭喺現場繼續播<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bsavc5l9QR4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dbsavc5l9QR4&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5Au0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=1ead9fd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bsavc5l9QR4</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:26:30.000Z","msg":"唔得<br />\n<br />\n果段錄音只係嗌mic行動既其中一部分<br />\n<br />\n呢個嗌mic行動只會出現一次<br />\n因為內容問題<br />\n<br />\n佢唔係普通既嗌mic<br />\n您將會聽到成個運動一直以來<br />\n第一次有人燃燒生命咁，響住香港人吶喊<br />\n佢唔係一種宣傳，所以佢只會出現一次"},{"pid":"921d393358f1a36e662a05db1efd82179d4eff9a","tid":1513181,"uid":131264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e4ff020f9a713a99f52fd00f8b3b40a9c55aba","tid":1513181,"uid":137871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"好想幫你手，不過自覺有其他更適合既人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:33:14.000Z","msg":"暫時都未有人主動聯絡我幫手<br />\n唔洗覺得幫唔到我<br />\n剩係陪我視察地理<br />\n又或者幫我做下關於大聲公/大喇叭既功課<br />\n已經幫左我好多<br />\n<br />\n我依家係831果日既遊行路線到試行緊<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔係大project來<br />\n可能20分鐘內，就會講晒全部內容<br />\n但您只要有心想幫我，聯絡我<br />\n我會畀您知道嗌mic既內容<br />\n您就會知道當日呢20分鐘所聽到既內容<br />\n會直接成為您地所有人係抗爭路上既心靈支柱"},{"pid":"336ca0f5eb5d507